  <summary date="2005-12-23T15:39:17Z" status="Introduced in House">Amtrak Board Leadership Enhancement Act - Amends federal transportation law to replace the Amtrak Reform Board with a reconstituted Board of Directors of Amtrak (effectively eliminating the Reform Board).

Revises former requirements for the composition and terms of the Board of Directors.

Allows members of the Amtrak Reform Board to continue to serve out their terms.</summary>
